 * Jenkinsfile — {{SERVICE_NAME}}
 * Generated from the react template.
 *
 * The shared library is loaded directly from the platform repo — no global
 * Jenkins configuration required. {{LIB_REPO_URL}} is the URL Jenkins uses
 * internally to clone the library (may differ from the host-facing Gitea URL
 * when Jenkins runs inside Docker/k3d).
